, and compliance documentation\"\n    },\n    {\n        \"name\": \"Service\",\n        \"description\": \"Service-specific documents, including client business reviews and the client's environment folder\",\n        \"children\": [\n            {\n                \"name\": \"Business Reviews\",\n                \"description\": \"Documents of our summaries and notes created during client business reviews\"\n            },\n            {\n                \"name\": \"Environment\",\n                \"description\": \"Articles regarding the client's environmental uniqueness- anything that either does not conform to our normal mold or is generally important to keep track of.\"\n            }\n        ]\n    }\n]\n-}}"}],"to":null,"when":"{{ SUCCEEDED }}"}],"packOverrides":[],"publishResultAs":"folder_definitions","retry":null,"runAsOrgId":null,"timeout":600,"transitionMode":"FOLLOW_ALL","with":null,"securitySchema":{}},{"id":"@@@workflow_task_id_ref5@@@","action":{"id":"@@@action_ref1@@@"},"humanSecondsSaved":0,"input":{},"isMocked":false,"join":0,"mockInput":{"mock_result":{}},"name":"filter_active_companies","next":[{"do":["@@@workflow_task_id_ref3@@@"],"from":null,"id":"@@@transition_id_ref5@@@","publish":[{"key":"active_companies","value":"{% set filtered = [c for c in CTX.raw_companies if not c.archived] %}{% if CTX.target_company_name %}{{ [c for c in filtered if c.name == CTX.target_company_name] }}{% else %}{{ filtered }}{% endif %}"}],"to":null,"when":"{{ CTX.raw_companies | length > 0 }}"}],"packOverrides":[],"publishResultAs":"active_companies","retry":null,"runAsOrgId":"","timeout":600,"transitionMode":"FOLLOW_ALL","with":null,"securitySchema":{"redact":{"input":[],"result":[]}}},{"id":"@@@workflow_task_id_ref6@@@","action":{"id":"@@@action_ref2@@@"},"humanSecondsSaved":0,"input":{"query_params":{"city":null,"name":null,"state":null,"website":null,"id_number":null,"phone_number":null,"max_result_size":null,"id_in_integration":null}},"isMocked":false,"join":0,"mockInput":{"mock_result":{}},"name":"list_hudu_companies","next":[{"do":["@@@workflow_task_id_ref5@@@"],"from":null,"id":"@@@transition_id_ref6@@@","publish":[{"key":"raw_companies","value":"{{ RESULT.result }}"}],"to":null,"when":"{{ SUCCEEDED }}"}],"packOverrides":[],"publishResultAs":"hudu_companies","retry":null,"runAsOrgId":"","timeout":600,"transitionMode":"FOLLOW_ALL","with":null,"securitySchema":{"redact":{"input":[],"result":[]}}}],"timeout":28800,"type":"STANDARD","varsSchema":{}},"nonfunctional_fields":{"description":"","name":"[BEZ - PROC] Docs: Seed Default Folders","notes[0].content":"## How to Add New Folders\n\nEdit the **Data Aliases** on the `define_folder_list` task's transition to add or modify folders.\n\n### Example Configuration:\n```json\n[\n  {\"name\": \"Network Documentation\", \"description\": \"Network diagrams, IP schemes, and configurations\"},\n  {\"name\": \"Security Policies\", \"description\": \"Security policies and compliance documentation\"},\n  {\"name\": \"Onboarding\", \"description\": \"New client onboarding documentation\"},\n  {\"name\": \"Runbooks\", \"description\": \"Standard operating procedures and runbooks\"}\n]\n```\n\n### Adding a New Folder:\nSimply add a new object to the list with:\n- `name` (required): The folder name\n- `description` (optional): Folder description\n\nThe workflow will automatically skip folders that already exist for each company.","notes[0].metadata":{"x":-23.62999999999994,"y":-6.689999999999941,"fill":"rgba(66, 158, 255, 0.08)","width":370,"height":103,"stroke":"rgba(66, 158, 255, 0.7)","padding":20,"task_ids":["019c96a119ed75a3a22ce52d53b62454"],"fillEnabled":true,"positioning_mode":"task_container","requires_auto_position":false},"notes[0].title":"📁 Folder Configuration","notes[1].content":"## Workflow Flow\n\n1. **Define Folders** - Configure the nested folder structure to deploy\n2. **List Companies** - Fetch all companies from Hudu\n3. **Filter Active** - Remove archived companies (and filter by target company if specified)\n4. **Check Existing** - Get existing folders for each company (with-items)\n5. **Flatten & Determine** - Flatten nested hierarchy with depth levels, exclude existing folders\n6. **Initialize** - Set current_depth=0, max_depth, and known folders list\n7. **Create at Depth** - Create all folders at current depth level (with-items)\n8. **Update & Check** - Add newly created folders to known list, increment depth\n9. **Loop** - If more depth levels exist, go back to step 7\n\n### Workflow Input\n| Parameter | Type | Required | Description |\n|-----------|------|----------|-------------|\n| `target_company_name` | String | No | If provided, only targets this specific Hudu company. Leave empty to target all active companies. |\n\n### Features:\n- ✅ Skips archived companies\n- ✅ Skips folders that already exist (idempotent)\n- ✅ **Supports unlimited nesting depth**\n- ✅ Processes folders level-by-level (parents before children)\n- ✅ Concurrent API calls (5 at a time per level)\n- ✅ Easy to add new folders via nested JSON structure\n- ✅ Optional single-company targeting","notes[1].metadata":{"x":-63.31000000000006,"y":108.71999999999991,"fill":"rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.08)","width":458,"height":356,"stroke":"rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.7)","padding":20,"task_ids":["019c96a178ea77f6b8d9ef6ee36d4922","019c96a194467d54bca5a565f1b91a2b","019c96a1b77f7dff8905de42792ddbc6","019c96a1d68278afb729398a1a1bb2a1","019c96ae6bbc76ffa1f7f59deb0e8d87","019c96a201107cc99dc20ddf95d805fc","019cb994402d7ebdbd6bc02340ddeae5"],"fillEnabled":true,"positioning_mode":"task_container","requires_auto_position":false},"notes[1].title":"🔄 Workflow Overview","parameters.target_company_name.description":"If provided, only targets this specific Hudu company by exact name. Leave empty to target all active companies.","parameters.target_company_name.label":"Target Company Name","tasks[0].description":"Action for flow control, logic, or data","tasks[0].metadata":{"x":0,"y":48